title: Summary of Damages and Rescues by Province, Pakistan Floods, 8.17.2010
name: Summary of Damages and Rescues by Province, Pakistan Floods, 8.17.2010
description:
This dataset displays information on the 2010 flooding damages and rescues in Pakistan by Province.

The information comes from the National Disaster Management Authority of Pakistan.

The data includes:

Persons Rescued

Injured

Houses Damaged

Deaths
